GLP-1 mimetics and cognition 
Habib Yaribeygi a, Ali Rashidy-Pour a,*, Stephen L. Atkin b, Tannaz Jamialahmadi c,d, 
Amirhossein Sahebkar e,f,g,h,** 
a Research Center of Physiology, Semnan University of Medical Sciences, Semnan, Iran 
